  <brief_title>The Effect of Vitamin B3 on Substrate Metabolism, Insulin Sensitivity, and Body Composition in Obese Men</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Nicotinamide Ribose (NR) on Substrate Metabolism, Insulin Sensitivity, and Body Composition in Obese Men - a Randomized, Placebo Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
